Package: chumby-player
Version: @VERSION@
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Jan <jan@simula.no>
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Depends: cage, mpv, pipewire-alsa, chumby-player-data
Description: Chumby control panel player (chumby-fork Ruffle kiosk)
 Runs the original Chumby Classic control panel under a patched Ruffle
 (cargo feature "chumby") inside a cage Wayland kiosk on tty1.
 Installing this package and enabling chumby-player.service turns the
 Pi into "player mode"; SSH stays available, and
 "systemctl disable --now chumby-player" is the escape hatch.
 .
 Dependencies on stock trixie libraries (libasound2, libudev1, ...)
 are not declared; the binary is a private cross-build verified on the
 target image, not a policy-compliant Debian package.
